<Paragraph>
In this sample, data from an Excel worksheet is exported to the data grid and the same data is imported into a new worksheet with styles. 
</Paragraph>

<Paragraph>
The <Bold>ImportDataTable</Bold> and <Bold>ExportDataTable</Bold> methods make it very easy to work with ADO.NET data tables. It takes just one line of code to import data from a spreadsheet to a data table and export the data from a data table into a spreadsheet.
</Paragraph>

